---
// El diferenciador — cómo ve tu cliente la cotización (mockup del link público /q/).
// Layout split: copy a la izquierda, mockup del link a la derecha.
---

<section class="cv">
    <div class="cv-inner">
        <div class="cv-text">
            <p class="cv-eyebrow reveal">LA EXPERIENCIA DE TU CLIENTE</p>
            <h2 class="cv-title reveal">Cada cotización se ve<br />como tu mejor venta.</h2>
            <p class="cv-p reveal">
                Tu cliente no recibe un PDF perdido en el correo. Recibe un link con tu
                logo, tus colores y tus datos — donde ve los productos, el total y aprueba
                con un botón. Profesional, en su celular, en segundos.
            </p>
            <ul class="cv-list">
                <li class="reveal"><span class="cv-check">✓</span> Con tu marca: logo, colores y datos fiscales</li>
                <li class="reveal"><span class="cv-check">✓</span> Aprueba o paga sin crear cuenta</li>
                <li class="reveal"><span class="cv-check">✓</span> Tú te enteras en el momento exacto en que la ve</li>
                <li class="reveal"><span class="cv-check">✓</span> Válida hasta la fecha que tú definas</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="cv-visual reveal-mockup">
            <div class="phone">
                <div class="phone-notch"></div>
                <div class="phone-screen">
                    <div class="ps-brand">
                        <div class="ps-logo">EZ</div>
                        <div>
                            <div class="ps-company">Distribuidora El Zarco</div>
                            <div class="ps-cot">Cotización COT-0148</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="ps-amount">
                        <span class="ps-amount-label">TOTAL</span>
                        <span class="editorial ps-amount-val">$196,469.20</span>
                        <span class="ps-amount-cur">MXN · IVA incluido · Net 30</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="ps-items">
                        <div class="ps-item"><span>Cemento gris 50kg ×120</span><span class="editorial">$21,840</span></div>
                        <div class="ps-item"><span>Varilla 3/8" ×340</span><span class="editorial">$57,290</span></div>
                        <div class="ps-item"><span>Block hueco ×2,400</span><span class="editorial">$34,080</span></div>
                        <div class="ps-item ps-more">+ 1 producto más</div>
                    </div>

                    <button class="ps-approve">Aprobar cotización</button>
                    <button class="ps-secondary">Descargar PDF</button>

                    <div class="ps-footer">Cotización válida hasta el 24 jun · vía <b>trato</b></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cv-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .cv {
        padding: 7rem 5%;
        background: var(--color-bg-soft);
        overflow: clip;
    }
    .cv-inner {
        max-width: 1120px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 0.85fr;
        gap: 5rem;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .cv-eyebrow {
        font-size: 0.65rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 3px;
        text-transform: uppercase; color: #888; margin: 0 0 1.2rem;
    }
    .cv-title {
        font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3.4vw, 2.9rem);
        font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.1; letter-spacing: -1.2px;
        color: var(--color-text); margin: 0 0 1.4rem;
    }
    .cv-p {
        font-size: 1.08rem; line-height: 1.65;
        color: var(--color-text-muted); margin: 0 0 2rem; max-width: 460px;
    }
    .cv-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
    .cv-list li {
        display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
        font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-text); font-weight: 500;
    }
    .cv-check {
        width: 24px; height: 24px; flex-shrink: 0;
        background: rgba(16,185,129,0.12); color: #059669;
        border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
        font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 700;
    }

    /* Phone mockup */
    .cv-visual { position: relative; display: flex; justify-content: center; }
    .cv-glow {
        position: absolute; inset: 10% 0;
        background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(10,25,47,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
        z-index: 0; filter: blur(20px);
    }
    .phone {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        width: 300px;
        background: #0a192f;
        border-radius: 42px;
        padding: 12px;
        box-shadow:
            0 2px 6px rgba(10,25,47,0.2),
            0 40px 80px -24px rgba(10,25,47,0.5),
            inset 0 0 0 2px rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }
    .phone-notch {
        position: absolute; top: 22px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
        width: 100px; height: 22px; background: #0a192f; border-radius: 100px; z-index: 3;
    }
    .phone-screen {
        background: #fff;
        border-radius: 32px;
        padding: 2.2rem 1.4rem 1.4rem;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1.1rem;
    }

    .ps-brand { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 11px; padding-top: 0.5rem; }
    .ps-logo {
        width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 11px;
        background: var(--color-blue-deep); color: #fff;
        display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
        font-weight: 800; font-size: 0.9rem; letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }
    .ps-company { font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 700; color: #0a192f; }
    .ps-cot { font-size: 0.72rem; color: #99a; margin-top: 1px; }

    .ps-amount {
        display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 4px;
        padding: 1.2rem; border-radius: 16px;
        background: var(--color-bg-soft);
        text-align: center;
    }
    .ps-amount-label { font-size: 0.6rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 2px; color: #aab; }
    .ps-amount-val { font-size: 2.1rem; color: #0a192f; line-height: 1; }
    .ps-amount-cur { font-size: 0.68rem; color: #889; font-weight: 500; }

    .ps-items { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }
    .ps-item {
        display: flex; justify-content: space-between;
        font-size: 0.8rem; color: #445;
    }
    .ps-item .editorial { color: #0a192f; }
    .ps-more { color: #99a; font-size: 0.74rem; }

    .ps-approve {
        background: var(--color-blue-deep); color: #fff;
        border: none; cursor: pointer;
        font-size: 0.92rem; font-weight: 600;
        padding: 14px; border-radius: 13px;
        font-family: var(--font-sans);
        box-shadow: 0 12px 28px -10px rgba(10,25,47,0.5);
    }
    .ps-secondary {
        background: none; border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
        color: #556; cursor: pointer;
        font-size: 0.88rem; font-weight: 600;
        padding: 12px; border-radius: 13px;
        font-family: var(--font-sans);
        margin-top: -0.4rem;
    }
    .ps-footer { font-size: 0.68rem; color: #aab; text-align: center; margin-top: 0.2rem; }
    .ps-footer b { color: #667; }

    @media (max-width: 860px) {
        .cv-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3.5rem; }
        .cv-p { max-width: 100%; }
    }
</style>
